Bangun!  - Hati-hati!  Bangun!

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.960
Bangun!  - Berdiri!  Neelam!

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:04.120
Ayo.  Tolong cepat.

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:08.000
Hati-hati!  Hati-hati!  Lakshmi, santai saja!
- Bawa dia ke sini!

00:08:08.080 --> 00:08:09.200
Kamu...
- Bawa dia ke sini.

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:11.040
Hei...
- Hati-hati.

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:17.400
Tante!  Bibi...
- Resi... Resi!

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:19.520
TIDAK!  Nelam, tidak!
- Tante!  Bibi... Bibi!

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:21.000
Bibi, hati-hati!  - Resi!

